I as well as you have been very upset with the way the current "balance" setup is. Therefore I decided to look at the AE mez's/stuns of the other realms. Here they are.<P><BR>MIDGARD<P>---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<BR>==Skald==<P>Skill Level: 32 Power Cost: 39 Casting Time: 0.00 sec. Duration: 24 sec Range: 12' Description: Enemy mesmerized. You must wait 30 seconds to cast again.<P>Skill Level: 42 Power Cost: 53 Casting Time: 0.00 sec. Duration: 29 sec Range: 12' Description: Enemy mesmerized. You must wait 30 seconds to cast again.<BR>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<BR>==Healer==<BR>  Mez's<BR>Skill Level: 34 Power Cost: 21 Casting Time: 3.00 sec. Duration: 52 sec Range: 25' Radius of Effect: 4 Description: Enemies in area mesmerized<P>Skill Level: 36 Power Cost: 24 Casting Time: 0.00 sec. Duration: 26 sec Range: 25' Radius of Effect: 2 Description: Enemies in area mesmerized<P>Skill Level: 44 Power Cost: 28 Casting Time: 3.00 sec. Duration: 1 min Range: 25' Radius of Effect: 4 Description: Enemies in area mesmerized<P>Skill Level: 47 Power Cost: 30 Casting Time: 0.00 sec. Duration: 31 sec Range: 25' Radius of Effect: 5 Description: Enemies in area mesmerized<P> Stuns<P>Skill Level: 32 Power Cost: 20 Casting Time: 2.50 sec. Duration: 9 sec Range: 25' Radius of Effect: 4 Description: Paralyzes all Enemies in affected area<P>Skill Level: 38 Power Cost: 24 Casting Time: 0.00 sec. Duration: 9 sec Range: 25' Radius of Effect: 2 Description: Paralyzes all Enemies in affected area<P>Skill Level: 42 Power Cost: 27 Casting Time: 2.50 sec. Duration: 10 sec Range: 25' Radius of Effect: 4 Description: Paralyzes all Enemies in affected area<P>Skill Level: 48 Power Cost: 31 Casting Time: 0.00 sec. Duration: 10 sec Range: 25' Radius of Effect: 5 Description: Paralyzes all Enemies in affected area<P>Skill Level: 50 Power Cost: 33 Casting Time: 2.50 sec. Duration: 11 sec Range: 25' Radius of Effect: 4 Description: Paralyzes all Enemies in affected area<BR>----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<P>HIBERNIA<P>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<P>==Bard==<P>Skill Level: 36 Power Cost: 23 Casting Time: 3.00 sec. Duration: 1 min Range: 25' Radius of Effect: 5 Description: Enemies in area mesmerized<P>Skill Level: 43 Power Cost: 27 Casting Time: 3.00 sec. Duration: 1.1 min Range: 25' Radius of Effect: 6 Description: Enemies in area mesmerized<BR>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<P>==Eldritch==<P>Skill Level: 37 Power Cost: 23 Casting Time: 3.00 sec. Duration: 26 sec Range: 25' Radius of Effect: 6 Description: Enemies in area mesmerized<P>Skill Level: 47 Power Cost: 30 Casting Time: 3.00 sec. Duration: 31 sec Range: 25' Radius of Effect: 7 Description: Enemies in area mesmerized<BR>-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<P>Albion<P>----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<BR>==Sorcerer==<P>Skill Level: 34 Power Cost: 16 Casting Time: 3.00 sec. Duration: 59 Range: 25' Radius of Effect: 6 Description: Enemies in area mesmerized<P>Skill Level: 44 Power Cost: 21 Casting Time: 3.00 sec. Duration: 1.2 Range: 25' Radius of Effect: 7 Description: Enemies in area mesmerized<BR>-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<BR>==Theurgst==<P>Skill Level: 30 Power Cost: 25 Casting Time: 3.00 sec. Duration: 23 sec Range: 21' Radius of Effect: 5 Description: Enemies in area mesmerized<P>Skill Level: 39 Power Cost: 33 Casting Time: 3.00 sec. Duration: 27 Range: 21' Radius of Effect: 5 Description: Enemies in area mesmerized<P>Skill Level: 49 Power Cost: 42 Casting Time: 3.00 sec. Duration: 32 sec Range: 21' Radius of Effect: 5 Description: Enemies in area mesmerized<P><BR> Ok now lets look at the closet spells a Sorcerer and Healer have per level.<P> Sorcerer Lvl 44 mez Power costs 7 less, Duration .2 longer, Range 3 more. This being the highest level AE mez a sorcerer has.<P> Now looking at Balance this looks fair, however these are not the only factors to take in. You also need to look at stuns since this is all part of tactics and is the opening spell used.<P> So combine the Healers lvl 44 Mez with the lvl 42 Stun u now have the starting battle spell taking .5 less time to cast, and thier combined duration is now 1.1.<P> Yes our mez has a longer duration yet we can never get it casted because of the quickness of the stuns.<P><BR> The speed and time duration combined with the AF and HP's all combine to make a very unbalancing factor for the other 2 realms.<P> This is why I think everyone is getting upset in RvR and why we here the famous "I was mez'd the whole fight" complaints all the time.<P> How can this be fixed? No idea  <IMG SRC="frown.gif" border="0"> You cannot just take a classes spell away from them for balancing issues. More resists for RvR? This could help but would also gimp our main spell also (as I am sure resist gear would be added to Midgard also).<P> Another thing I noticed doing RvR. One Healer is able to completely wipe out a full group of invaders by keeping them mez/stuned while another person activtes guards inside the keep to come kill them all (not sure how guards are activated but there seems to be a way).<P> Now I know when I am in a keep I cannot mez anyone standing right at the front door. I get the message "Your target is not in View" or "Your target is to far away".<P> Are these bug/exploits that someone else has brought up before?<P> Well anyway there my opinions and the facts as they stand.
