<IMG SRC="http://forums.castersrealm.com/daoc/profile_ubb6.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="Profile for Ellejienne"></A> &nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://" target=_new><IMG SRC="http://forums.castersrealm.com/daoc/homepage.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="Author's Homepage"></A> &nbsp;  &nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://forums.castersrealm.com/cgi-bin/daoc/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=edit_post&f=21&t=000326&reply_num=000003&u=00001669"><IMG SRC="http://forums.castersrealm.com/daoc/edit_ubb6.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="Edit/Delete Post"></A> &nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://forums.castersrealm.com/cgi-bin/daoc/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=reply&f=21&t=000326&replyto=000003"><IMG SRC="http://forums.castersrealm.com/daoc/quote_ubb6.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="Reply With Quote"></A>
